Khan,Academy,is,a,non,profit,educational,organization,that,provides,a,free,online,education,to,anyone,anywhere,The,site,contains,over,online,videos,covering,subjects,from,finance,and,physics,to,math,and,art,The,API,gives,developers,access,to,nearly,all,of,the,data,stored,on,the,site,categorized,by,Playlists,Within,each,playlist,users,can,discover,videos,or,use,the,playlists,to,get,information,about,the,exercises,for,each,The,API,also,returns,information,about,badges,awarded,via,the,exercise,dashboard,The,API,methods,are,split,into,topics,videos,exercises,badges,and,user,data,The,API,uses,RESTful,calls,and,responses,are,formatted,in,JSON